      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion wedges</strong>, <strong>carrot discs</strong>,<strong> dried oregano</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with your<strong> beef stock mix</strong>,<strong> chopped tomatoes </strong>and <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and season generously with<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, then top with the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
