            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the dish in the oven, covered, for an initial 30 min or until the potatoes are tender and everything's cooked through</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 5,
